&lt;p&gt;ERROR 14:36:49,797 Fatal exception in thread Thread&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;WRITE-/10.228.243.191,5,main&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
